---
// Horizontal bar chart for top technologies
// Rendered client-side with Chart.js, responds to location filter
---

<section class="mb-12" aria-labelledby="tech-demand-heading">
  <h2 id="tech-demand-heading" class="text-zinc-50 text-base font-medium mb-1">
    Technology Demand
  </h2>
  <p class="text-sm text-zinc-500 mb-4" id="tech-demand-subtitle">
    Top 20 technologies across all of New Zealand
  </p>

  <div id="tech-legend" class="flex flex-wrap gap-x-4 gap-y-1 mb-4 text-xs">
  </div>

  <div class="relative" style="height: 520px;">
    <canvas id="tech-demand-chart"></canvas>
  </div>
</section>
